node.text:
Happy Friday IG fam! I recently shared some of my go-to meals, but I wanted to take it a step further and add in my vitamin and supplement routine. My lifestyle choices are all about creating sustainable habits that are not extreme, but easy to follow. 𝐇𝐞𝐫𝐞 𝟓 𝐠𝐞𝐧𝐞𝐫𝐚𝐥 𝐭𝐢𝐩𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐈 𝐥𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐛𝐲:

1️⃣- Practice portion control by using smaller dinner plates vs. larger ones

2️⃣- Eliminate sweets and minimize unhealthy snacking 

3️⃣- Incorporate a daily multivitamin & probiotic!... I use @gnclivewell Women’s multivitamin energy & metabolism and @gnclivewell women’s probiotic solutions help with improving my energy levels and balancing out the good bacteria in my gut

4️⃣- Incorporate fish oil into your lifestyle! I use @gnclivewell triple strength fish oil because it includes tons of benefits such as heart, brain, and eye health. In addition to filling the gaps in my nutrition. 

5️⃣- Drink lots of water and No heavy meals past 9:00 P.M.

𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐛𝐞𝐥𝐨𝐰 ⤵️ 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐪𝐮𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 & 𝐢𝐟 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐰𝐚𝐧𝐭 𝐦𝐨𝐫𝐞 𝐯𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐨𝐬 𝐥𝐢𝐤𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 !

𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐛𝐞𝐥𝐨𝐰 ⤵️ 𝐢𝐟 𝐲𝐨𝐮’𝐫𝐞 𝐠𝐢𝐯𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐚 𝐭𝐫𝐲! ... 𝐔𝐬𝐞 𝐦𝐲 𝐜𝐨𝐝𝐞 ‘𝐂𝐎𝐂𝐎’ 𝐚𝐭 𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐜𝐤𝐨𝐮𝐭
⠀
Happy Wednesday beautiful people! I’m back with another quick & yummy smoothie recipe that can be used as a meal replacement, or to supplement your nutrition routine. I paired the most yummy plant-based protein from @tru_supplements [Coconut macaron flavor]  with some of my favorite ingredients.
⠀
𝐒𝐦𝐨𝐨𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐞 𝐈𝐧𝐠𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬 👇🏾:
✓ 1 scoop of coconut macaron plant-based protein 🌱 @tru_supplements 
✓ 1 full tablespoon of nut butter
✓ 1/2 cup of ice
✓ Handful of blueberries
✓ 1 banana
✓ Water
⠀

𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐛𝐞𝐥𝐨𝐰 ⤵️ 𝐢𝐟 𝐲𝐨𝐮’𝐫𝐞 𝐠𝐢𝐯𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐚 𝐭𝐫𝐲!

Happy Tuesday beautiful people!! If you love coconut or pineapple as much as I do... this is the perfect smoothie recipe for YOU! I paired the most yummy plant-based protein from @tru_supplements [Coconut macaron flavor] with my favorite frozen fruits. 

I also whipped up a quick 2- minute go to snack for you guys using @tru_supplements Nut Butter 🥜😋... I’m a big fan of quick & healthy snacks! The biggest plus is that combined, they both fill you up and taste soooo good!... It’s a WIN- WIN 🤟🏽

𝐒𝐦𝐨𝐨𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐞 𝐈𝐧𝐠𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬:
✓ 1 scoop of coconut macaron plant-based protein 🌱 @tru_supplements 
✓ 1/2 cup of ice
✓ 1/2 cup of dairy free unsweetened milk 
✓ Handful of frozen pineapples 
✓ Handful of frozen blueberries

𝟐- 𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐮𝐭𝐞 𝐬𝐧𝐚𝐜𝐤 𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬:
✓ Nut butter by @tru_supplements 
✓ 1 rice cake

________________________________________________________
Happy Tuesday IG fam ❤️ This past weekend I attended the LA @thefitexpo and felt encouraged to hit some pull-ups at the @usnavy booth! [I hit 10 by the grace of God 🙏🏽]...Believe it or not my strength fluctuates depending on my goals and it’s been a while since I’ve consistently focused on calisthenics. [Shoutout to bae for the push @duke 😘]
____
So I just wanted to share this clip as a reminder that your fitness journey is not a seamless uphill process. All that matters is your ability to remain consistent! Everything we do in life is about a CONSISTENT EFFORT. So don’t be afraid to challenge yourself even when things feel intimidating because if it doesn’t challenge you, it won’t change you 🙌🏽 #pullups #fitnessmotivation 
________________________________________________________

𝐒𝐰𝐞𝐚𝐭𝐲 𝐟𝐚𝐭- 𝐛𝐮𝐫𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐇𝐈𝐈𝐓 𝐰𝐨𝐫𝐤𝐨𝐮𝐭 💦#𝐆𝐍𝐂𝐏𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐧𝐞𝐫 [𝐒𝐀𝐕𝐄 📁 + 𝐒𝐇𝐀𝐑𝐄 + 𝐂𝐎𝐌𝐌𝐄𝐍𝐓 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐟𝐚𝐯𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐭𝐞 𝐦𝐨𝐯𝐞 ⤵️]
⠀
Happy Friday IG fam! I’m back from vacation and it’s time to burn off all the food I indulged in. During the summer, my goal is to turn up the cardio and drop dead weight. I’ve been using a fat burner called 𝐁𝐞𝐲𝐨𝐧𝐝 𝐑𝐚𝐰 𝐁𝐮𝐫𝐧 𝐌𝐅 from @gnclivewell to take my body goals to the NEXT LEVEL and I am in love with the results! 
 
Beyond Raw Burn MF has 𝟐 𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐜𝐚𝐟𝐟𝐞𝐢𝐧𝐞, along with Huperzine A and fully dosed L-theanine to help increase your focus, and keep your head in the right zone for pushing through a high intensity workout like this 🔥 
 
𝐓𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐢𝐬 𝐚 𝐌𝐔𝐒𝐓 𝐇𝐀𝐕𝐄, 𝐢𝐧 𝐚𝐝𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐭𝐨 𝐚 𝐬𝐨𝐥𝐢𝐝 𝐰𝐨𝐫𝐤𝐨𝐮𝐭 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐧𝐮𝐭𝐫𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐩𝐥𝐚𝐧 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐛𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐮𝐥𝐭𝐬. 𝐆𝐫𝐚𝐛 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐬 𝐧𝐨𝐰!  @gnclivewell #GNCPartner
⠀
🎥: @broll.productions

node.text:
Happy Friday IG fam! I recently shared some of my go-to meals, but I wanted to take it a step further and add in my vitamin and supplement routine. My lifestyle choices are all about creating sustainable habits that are not extreme, but easy to follow. 𝐇𝐞𝐫𝐞 𝟓 𝐠𝐞𝐧𝐞𝐫𝐚𝐥 𝐭𝐢𝐩𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐈 𝐥𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐛𝐲:

1️⃣- Practice portion control by using smaller dinner plates vs. larger ones

2️⃣- Eliminate sweets and minimize unhealthy snacking 

3️⃣- Incorporate a daily multivitamin & probiotic!... I use @gnclivewell Women’s multivitamin energy & metabolism and @gnclivewell women’s probiotic solutions help with improving my energy levels and balancing out the good bacteria in my gut

4️⃣- Incorporate fish oil into your lifestyle! I use @gnclivewell triple strength fish oil because it includes tons of benefits such as heart, brain, and eye health. In addition to filling the gaps in my nutrition. 

5️⃣- Drink lots of water and No heavy meals past 9:00 P.M.

𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐛𝐞𝐥𝐨𝐰 ⤵️ 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐪𝐮𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 & 𝐢𝐟 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐰𝐚𝐧𝐭 𝐦𝐨𝐫𝐞 𝐯𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐨𝐬 𝐥𝐢𝐤𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 !

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 𝐂𝐇𝐀𝐍𝐄𝐋 𝐃𝐄𝐋𝐈𝐒𝐒𝐄𝐑 in Thankful, Grateful, Blessed with @chaneldelisser, and @underground_nyc. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
🌟 𝟏  𝐌 𝐈 𝐋 𝐋 𝐈 𝐎 𝐍  𝐒𝐓𝐑𝐎𝐍𝐆 𝐁𝐀𝐁𝐘𝐘𝐘𝐘 🌟
⠀
𝐃𝐫𝐨𝐩 𝐬𝐨𝐦𝐞 ♥️♥️♥️ 𝐢𝐧 𝐦𝐲 𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬 𝐈𝐆 𝐟𝐚𝐦!
⠀
Whewwww 🎉 I still remember the days I prayed for what I have now. I started my Instagram in 2012 and I’d be lying if I said that I saw this coming. For me, it’s more than “followers”— you guys are really my online family. Y’all support me, cheer for me, hold me accountable, and really keep me going. I’m forever grateful for ALL OF YOU!… The love is realllll! Keep rockin with me, and I’ll keep showing up for you.
⠀
𝑳𝒐𝒗𝒆 𝑪𝒐𝒄𝒐 💋
📸: @underground_nyc 
⠀

𝐂𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐡𝐞𝐚𝐥𝐭𝐡𝐲 𝐡𝐚𝐛𝐢𝐭𝐬, 𝐧𝐨𝐭 𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬!
⠀
𝐒𝐰𝐢𝐩𝐞 𝐥𝐞𝐟𝐭 ⬅️ 𝐭𝐨 𝐬𝐞𝐞 𝐬𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐦𝐲 𝐭𝐲𝐩𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥 𝐛𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐤𝐟𝐚𝐬𝐭 / 𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐜𝐡 / 𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐧𝐞𝐫 𝐦𝐞𝐚𝐥𝐬!
⠀
Happy Tuesday beautiful people! I’ve been getting lots of DM’s about my meals and portion sizes. This is a glimpse of what I eat on a daily basis. I’m currently using the meal plan from my online program — Coco Fitness. If you need help with your nutrition, I got you! … SAVE this post & Comment with questions ⬇️
⠀
🔗 𝐆𝐫𝐚𝐛 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐩𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐨𝐧𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐳𝐞𝐝 𝐦𝐞𝐚𝐥 𝐩𝐥𝐚𝐧 𝐚𝐭 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐥𝐢𝐧𝐤 𝐢𝐧 𝐦𝐲 𝐛𝐢𝐨! 𝐅𝐮𝐥𝐥 𝐠𝐫𝐨𝐜𝐞𝐫𝐲 𝐥𝐢𝐬𝐭, 𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐩𝐞𝐬, & 𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐨𝐮𝐭 𝐨𝐩𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 𝐚𝐯𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞 🍽
⠀

𝐃𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐲 𝐚𝐟𝐟𝐢𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧: 𝐌𝐢 𝐫𝐮𝐧 𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬. 𝐓𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐧𝐮𝐡 𝐫𝐮𝐧 𝐦𝐢🔥 [𝐁𝐨𝐨𝐭𝐲 🍑 + 𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠]

⠀

⠀
